  "detailed_description": "<h1>Get Wrecked!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/cf62467d3fd65f87951634bf0395b21a.avif?t=1756484169\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready for Wrecked, where racing and chaos collide. Perform outrageous stunts, smash cars, and embrace total destruction. With insane driving and demolition, every race is a thrilling ride into mayhem!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ab8f1788cc33e9e567940e63b6f4160d.poster.avif?t=1756484169\" width=648 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ab8f1788cc33e9e567940e63b6f4160d.webm?t=1756484169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ab8f1788cc33e9e567940e63b6f4160d.mp4?t=1756484169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Wrecked!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your super smashing power to demolish everything in your path and master the art of unfair stunts with your insane driving skills, navigating through chaotic environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ae987040dd8df4c082e1d58eba152131.poster.avif?t=1756484169\" width=646 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ae987040dd8df4c082e1d58eba152131.webm?t=1756484169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553810/extras/ae987040dd8df4c082e1d58eba152131.mp4?t=1756484169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 40 exhilarating levels, you’ll race through a variety of wild environments like ramps, bridges, and even running trains. Experience the thrill of jaw-dropping front and back flips!</p>",
